&lt;li&gt;Loud environment—hearing protection required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on, team-oriented environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities to learn new skills and grow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to safety and quality&lt;/li&gt;
