&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the go‑to product authority for MQ Power mobile diesel generators and related industrial power products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and interpret product documentation, drawings, specifications, and technical data to provide accurate and timely responses to customers, dealers, and internal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain expert‑level knowledge of the MQ Power portfolio, including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Denyo / DMC Generators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Studio Generators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portable Generators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Container Generators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MQ Acecube fuel tanks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refurbished Generators and related systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support new product introductions, internal training, and organization‑wide knowledge sharing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
