&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales and Engineering to define scope, support quoting, and execute custom generator solutions efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track progress, align stakeholders, and help remove roadblocks to keep CPRs moving forward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross‑Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
